This is both cardio and strength, imo practically the perfect workout for health, toning and weight loss. Cardio is useful for heart health and burning calories but it's more important to build muscle (toning) as a) it looks better and b) muscle burns more calories at rest. A mix of cardio and strength is ideal, but you also need to ensure you don't overeat or drink your calories.

Moving your body is helpful to loose weight no matter the style of workout. It’s always a good idea to vary your workouts to keep your body and muscles challenged. Find workouts you find fun in order to stay consistent :) good luck on your journey!
